snippet.title: NO QUARANTINE FOR CHRISTMAS FANTASY | original covid song by her habits
snippet.description:
Continuing to be a two-tier society, no-longer-a-democracy Chinada, *cough*, I mean CANADA is now also taking away those freedoms once granted to the FIRST-CLASS citzens! It's lockdown covid pandemic new variant Moronic madness here in the communist capital of North America. And I got something to say about it in this original covid Christmas song!

#Covid19 #Omicron #lockdown #FreeBC #FreeCanada

♪ check out my other covid song "TROUBLE" I performed live at a local freedom rally https://youtu.be/v1z_wkjblT8♪ 
Instagram📸@herhabitschannel  https://www.instagram.com/herhabitschannel/
TikTok⏰@herhabitschannel https://www.tiktok.com/@herhabitschannel

Music Attributions:

Jingle Bells 7 by Kevin MacLeod is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 licence. https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
Artist: http://incompetech.com/

Hip Hop Christmas by Twin Musicom is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 licence. https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
Artist: http://www.twinmusicom.org/

---------------------------------

lyrics:

No quarantine for Christmas
I don't care what Bonnie Henry says
she's not my mommy, Trudeau's not my daddy
so why would I be grounded?

There's a new variant for Christmas
but I'm not scared no matter what the mainstream media says
Omicron, it's mild they say but you're still gonna die anyway
Tell me, why they tryin' so hard to take our freedom?

All these politicians asking like they care
about our health
All these figureheads still tryin' to make us scared

Well let me tell you something Bonnie...
you're keeping the people of B.C. in a constant state of anxiety
and that's cause for disease!

No isolating for Christmas
I don't care what Theresa Tam says
she's not my mommy, Trudeau's not my daddy 
so why would I listen to them?

We still celebrated Christmas
with each other face to face
cause if you're sick you won't wanna leave your bed
but the rest of us aren't all diseased so instead
we danced the night away

All the sheep fast asleep in their pen
they missed out
All these happy people together again

Cause covid's not gonna stop Christmas
this government grinch can't take my freedoms away
vaccinated or unvaccinated, we'll still celebrate 
so Merry Christmas to you from me

Merry Christmas
